with Mrs. Dunbar.

12:07.694 --> 12:09.093
She's new
and she's really tough.

12:09.195 --> 12:10.663
She was in World War ll.

12:10.764 --> 12:12.823
As a nurse?

12:12.932 --> 12:15.060
No, a tank.

12:15.168 --> 12:17.660
After she locks up,
she runs a bed check.

12:17.771 --> 12:19.398
The beds are still here.

12:19.506 --> 12:21.065
How long do we have?

12:21.174 --> 12:23.233
Oh, not that long.

12:23.343 --> 12:25.971
