floor, maybe a half an hour.

12:26.079 --> 12:27.240
Half an hour!

12:27.347 --> 12:30.009
But if she starts up here,
it could be two seconds.

12:30.116 --> 12:32.084
-(knocking on door)
- She's early!

12:33.286 --> 12:34.583
