12:35.789 --> 12:37.223
Mmm!
What are you doing?

12:37.324 --> 12:39.122
I'm not getting kicked out
for just talking.

12:49.336 --> 12:50.235
(knocking at door)

12:50.337 --> 12:51.702
Mm! Do something!

12:51.805 --> 12:53.170
Under the bed!
Uh, in the closet!

12:53.273 --> 12:54.832
All right, all right.
Stay calm.

12:54.941 --> 12:56.306
Keep a cool head.

12:56.409 --> 12:58.400
I'm jumping out the window!

12:59.612 --> 13:00.773
Can't jump, it's stuck.

13:00.880 --> 13:03.008
- Oh, in-in here.
- Right.

13:03.116 --> 13:04.845
- And try not to wrinkle
anything. -All right.

13:05.719 --> 13:07.346
CHRISTY:
Lori Beth, open up!

13:07.454 --> 13:09.445
It's me, Christy!

13:10.957 --> 13:13.324
- Thank heavens you're alone...
-...Leona's still sick.

13:19.733 --> 13:21.997
So this is where
you want me to hide.

13:22.102 --> 13:23.695
I tell you, very good choice.

13:23.803 --> 13:25.464
The more, the merrier.

13:25.572 --> 13:27.438
Hey, don't I know you?

13:27.540 --> 13:29.804
I don't know, I...
fixed my hair and my tooth...

13:29.909 --> 13:31.434
No, no, no, no, no,
the "liberry."

13:31.544 --> 13:33.774
So where's, uh...

13:33.880 --> 13:35.871
Uh-huh.

13:38.218 --> 13:39.117
